These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, scooter, motorbike, car, bus, ship, train
7 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg, bridge, billiard, canasta
 1. the person playing canasta is the person driving the car##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 3. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 5. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
 6. the person driving the roller is not the person playing backgammon##6
 7. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 9. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person playing backgammon##7
10. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the ship##1
11. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
12. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
13. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the train##1
14. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person playing scrabble##7
15. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
16. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
17. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
18. the person driving the train is the person playing monopoly##1
19. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
20. the person driving the car is not the person playing billiard##6
21. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
22. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Transport           | ship | motorbike | train | scooter  | bus  | car | roller    |
| Game   | backgammon   | scrabble   | monopoly   | mah-jongg | bridge | canasta        | billiard |

