.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, march, may, december, january, october, september
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, soccer, cycling, sailing, surfing, biathlon
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
13. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
14. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
15. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
16. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Birthday   | september | december | may    | march | january | november | october |
| Sport     | ice-hockey     | surfing   | climbing | sailing | cycling       | soccer        | biathlon      |

